      • currentGrade

        public double currentGrade()
        Returns the current subject grade. The calculation is made like this: If the sum of the given grades is 100 it calculates currentGrade * (percentage/100). Else, it calculates currentGrade * (percentage/gradedPercentage).
        Returns:
        Current subject grade
